            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changed

### CLI & Back-end updates
- Added option to manage auto updates via sparkle
- Cleaned up CLI `--help`
- Fixed a LOT of issues and managed to get Sparkle updates without having to open the entire UI.
- Fixed the window by giving it a title, not allowing duplicate windows, preventing a separate panel for settings.
- Lots of bug fixes under the hood.
]]></description>
